data.description: Rare ranch-style in the coveted Embassy Hill neighborhood! Light, bright, and airy two-bedroom with beautiful ceramic tile throughout, spacious living room, and family room connected seamlessly to the outdoor lanai for indoor/outdoor entertaining. Recently renovated bathrooms, large kitchen with ample cabinets, counter space flex space perfect for gatherings or office, and large lot with excellent curb appeal.     The oversized covered porch with a pass-through window to the kitchen opens to the paved patio, perfect for bonfires and gatherings! Close to great beach locations with lots of shopping and entertainment easily accessible! Schedule a showing today!!!
